  <h2>How to Use AI Comparison Platform</h2>
  
  <h3>Getting Started</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Create an account or login to your existing account</li>
    <li>Navigate to the home page to submit queries</li>
    <li>Enter your question in the text area</li>
    <li>Click "Compare Responses" to see AI model outputs</li>
  </ol>
  
  <h3>Understanding the Results</h3>
  <p>After submitting a query, you'll receive:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Gemini Response:</strong> Google's latest AI model output</li>
    <li><strong>Llama Response:</strong> Meta's open-source model output</li>
    <li><strong>Deepseek Response:</strong> Deepseek's specialized model output</li>
    <li><strong>Semantic Comparison:</strong> An AI-generated analysis highlighting key differences</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h3>Query History</h3>
  <p>Your last 10 queries are automatically saved and can be accessed from the home page.</p>
  
  <h3>Profile Management</h3>
  <p>Update your profile information and password from the Profile page.</p>
